com.yworks.yfiles.layout.seriesparallel

Class EdgeLayoutDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yworks.yfiles.layout.seriesparallel.EdgeLayoutDescriptor

  • public class EdgeLayoutDescriptor
extends Object
    An EdgeLayoutDescriptor provides routing details for an edge that are considered by SeriesParallelLayout.

    Such an EdgeLayoutDescriptor can either be specified for a single edge or shared by several edges. It is assigned by registering a IDataProvider with key SeriesParallelLayout.EDGE_LAYOUT_DESCRIPTOR_DPKEY. If no IDataProvider is registered with this key, a default descriptor is used.

    See Also:
    SeriesParallelLayout.EDGE_LAYOUT_DESCRIPTOR_DPKEY, SeriesParallelLayout.getDefaultEdgeLayoutDescriptor()
